Dialogue: 8,0:23:09.04,0:23:13.37,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}羽蛇神
Dialogue: 8,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.20,ED - CN,,0,0,990,,{\fad(200,350)\blur1\c&HC187DC&\3c&HFFFFFF&}嘎嘎嘎
Dialogue: 8,0:23:14.94,0:23:20.68,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}一起吃的炒饭
Dialogue: 8,0:23:17.84,0:23:20.68,ED - CN,,0,0,990,,{\fad(200,350)\blur1\c&HC187DC&\3c&HFFFFFF&}炒饭
Dialogue: 8,0:23:20.68,0:23:24.40,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}又多写了一页
Dialogue: 8,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.60,ED - CN,,0,0,990,,{\fad(200,350)\blur1\c&HC187DC&\3c&HFFFFFF&}好开心
Dialogue: 8,0:23:26.60,0:23:30.28,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}走过一天天的夏天
Dialogue: 8,0:23:30.28,0:23:33.94,ED - CN,,0,0,990,,{\fad(200,350)\blur1\c&HC187DC&\3c&HFFFFFF&}明天也要
Dialogue: 8,0:23:32.45,0:23:38.82,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}六个脚印
Dialogue: 8,0:23:36.14,0:23:38.83,ED - CN,,0,0,990,,{\fad(200,350)\blur1\c&HC187DC&\3c&HFFFFFF&}一起
Dialogue: 7,0:22:22.12,0:22:28.00,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}セミとニワトリのおはよう
Dialogue: 7,0:22:28.00,0:22:33.89,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}思い出が始まる
Dialogue: 7,0:22:33.89,0:22:39.73,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}手書きの未来眺めて
Dialogue: 7,0:22:39.73,0:22:45.59,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}得意げに笑った
Dialogue: 7,0:22:45.59,0:22:54.94,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}これは魔法の絵日記
Dialogue: 7,0:22:57.33,0:23:01.68,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}手作り絵本
Dialogue: 7,0:23:00.25,0:23:04.44,ED - JP,,0,0,940,,{\fad(200,350)\blur2\c&HC187DC&\3c&HFFFFFF&}おとーさんさく
Dialogue: 7,0:23:03.17,0:23:07.37,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)\blur3}だましぶねのおりがみ
Dialogue: 7,0:23:06.10,0:23:10.31,ED - JP,,0,0,940,,{\fad(200,350)\blur2\c&HC187DC&\3c&HFFFFFF&}ふしぎどうして
